Invocation Name: compliment giver
des: We all have bad days. Sometimes you need just need a reminder of how awesome you are. When your best friend, boss, or significant other just can't come up with a satisfying enough compliment, ask Alexa. The Compliment Giver will give you the genuine and heartfelt encouragement you need to make it through your day!
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
